:true}]},{"id":"96","lang":"en","image":"\u003Cimg typeof=\u0022foaf:Image\u0022 src=\u0022https:\/\/myaccount.blood.ca\/sites\/dwp\/files\/eligibility_question\/icon-tattoo-or-piercing.svg\u0022 width=\u0022600\u0022 height=\u0022600\u0022 alt=\u0022\u0022 \/\u003E","requirement":"\u003Cp\u003EHave you had a \u003Cstrong\u003Etattoo or piercing\u003C\/strong\u003E in the last \u003Cstrong\u003Ethree months\u003C\/strong\u003E?\u003C\/p\u003E","requirementMoreInfo":"\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible\/abcs-eligibility#tattoos\u0022\u003EMore information\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","affirmation":"\u003Cp\u003EI have \u003Cstrong\u003Enot had\u003C\/strong\u003E a \u003Cstrong\u003Etattoo or piercing\u003C\/strong\u003E in the last \u003Cstrong\u003Ethree months\u003C\/strong\u003E.\u003C\/p\u003E","affirmationMoreInfo":"","ineligible":"\u003Cp\u003EUnfortunately, you are not able to donate blood right now. Learn more about \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible\/abcs-eligibility#tattoos\u0022\u003Ewhen you will be able to start saving lives\u003C\/a\u003E. In the meantime, ever thought of \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/ways-donate\/volunteering\u0022\u003Ebecoming a volunteer\u003C\/a\u003E?\u003C\/p\u003E","viewInfoUrl":"[cbs-site:blood]\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible\/abcs-eligibility#tattoos","options":[{"id":"yes","value":"Yes","fail":true},{"id":"no","value":"No","fail":false}]},{"id":"98","lang":"en","image":"\u003Cimg typeof=\u0022foaf:Image\u0022 src=\u0022https:\/\/myaccount.blood.ca\/sites\/dwp\/files\/eligibility_question\/icon-foreign-travel.svg\u0022 width=\u0022600\u0022 height=\u0022600\u0022 alt=\u0022\u0022 \/\u003E","requirement":"\u003Cp\u003EHave you \u003Cstrong\u003Etravelled outside of Canada, the continental USA, Antarctica or Europe\u003C\/strong\u003E in the last \u003Cstrong\u003E3 weeks\u003C\/strong\u003E?\u003C\/p\u003E","requirementMoreInfo":"\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENote: Some countries have a waiting period of \u003Cstrong\u003E21 days or longer\u003C\/strong\u003E. If you travelled to a malaria-risk area, the wait may be longer. Please call \u003Ca href=\u0022tel:1-888-236-6283\u0022\u003E1-888-2-DONATE\u003C\/a\u003E (1-888-236-6283) or tap \u003Cstrong\u003EMore Information\u003C\/strong\u003E below to check travel eligibility criteria. If you\u2019ve had malaria more than 6 months ago or are in the waiting period to donate whole blood or platelets because of travel to a malaria-risk country, you may be eligible to donate source plasma. \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible-donate-blood\/abcs-eligibility\/travel\u0022\u003EMore information.\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/em\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","affirmation":"\u003Cp\u003EI have \u003Cstrong\u003Enot travelled outside of Canada, the continental USA, Antarctica or Europe\u003C\/strong\u003E in the last \u003Cstrong\u003E3 weeks\u003C\/strong\u003E.\u003C\/p\u003E","affirmationMoreInfo":"\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENote: Some countries have a waiting period of \u003Cstrong\u003E21 days or longer\u003C\/strong\u003E. If you travelled to a malaria-risk area, the wait may be longer. Please call \u003Ca href=\u0022tel:1-888-236-6283\u0022\u003E1-888-2-DONATE\u003C\/a\u003E (1-888-236-6283) or tap \u003Cstrong\u003EMore Information\u003C\/strong\u003E below to check travel eligibility criteria. If you\u2019ve had malaria more than 6 months ago or are in the waiting period to donate whole blood or platelets because of travel to a malaria-risk country, you may be eligible to donate source plasma. \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible-donate-blood\/abcs-eligibility\/travel\u0022\u003EMore information.\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/em\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","ineligible":"\u003Cp\u003EDepending on what countries you have visited and for how long, you may be able to donate blood. \u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/blood.ca\/en\/blood\/am-i-eligible\/